<br>
1.  Get a good monk friend or a char with a 46 + monk twink to get his monk in there and FD near golem then log on every once and a while, this is the most effective and easiest way if ya got a friend with a 46 monk that he/she wouldn't mind not usin for a while heh<br>
<br>
2.  Seeing as #1 isn't a possiblity for most, do this...<br>
Get a cleric with rez/rev and a high level druid friend or ranger or bard friend, preferably level 60.  Not sure about you're server, but every other character on quellious is a druid heh, so shouldn't be too hard to find one.  Then, get outside of fear and have the cleric kill the ranger/druid/bard and then rez the ranger/druid/bard.  May want to just have the person kill themself so they dont have to deal with limited rez time on duel corpse.  Anyway, once the character is rezed back to their bod, have them leave everything on corpse.  Then, get the person buffed up good, and send em into fear NAKED.  After they zone in, start casting rez.  Have the ranger/druid/bard check track very quickly for golem, as you can see golem on track from portal with only a limited track skill.  After they check, have them click yes to be rezed out.<br>
<br>
Rapiki Fizzlesanddies<br>
Level 56 wizard<br>
Quellious<br>
