Come down through the right side of the graveyard and stay away from the FFs and spiders, since most of those see invis.  Run till you see the golem, then cut directly back through the middle of the graveyard (this time avoiding amys) and run through the TT structure where you'll have a few seconds while the mobs mess around trying to path across so you can gate.<br>
<br>
